sentence: In early trading on Thursday, shares of Home Depot topped the list of the day's best performing Dow Jones Industrial Average components, trading up 1.4%.
Year to date, Home Depot has lost about 3.9% of its value.
And the worst performing Dow component thus far on the day is Cisco Systems, trading down 6.0%.
Cisco Systems is showing a gain of 9.2% looking at the year to date performance.
Two other components making moves today are Wal-Mart Stores, trading down 3.0%, and JPMorgan Chase, trading up 1.3% on the day.
